Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是客人灌你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能喝太多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都要搞到我來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是心懷感激的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個這麼能幹的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱荻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱荻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱荻·狄文思是在這裡死的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都稱呼你Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從朱荻的夥伴那裡聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你在到處殺害美國的黑幫成員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真正的殺手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殺手對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺手Phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  給你這些錢幫我殺光他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上在那暗巷的人  開槍的人  本來要拿到這錢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓朱荻死去的傢伙們  把他們一個不剩地殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱荻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識了那個Phanom了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二一定會幫朱荻報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那500萬美元…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有500萬是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不夠的部分也就只有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點錢  你也能夠賺到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就暫時做我的助手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  做玲二的助手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能親眼目睹為朱荻報仇的那一刻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  必須獲得一樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑一件最想要的不就完事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊  這裡的衣服都很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要選一件的話  也就說要放棄其它的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  這不是一生一次的購物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想要的話  就再帶你來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以今天你就挑一件你現在想穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  吶  可愛嗎？  合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣輕飄飄的衣服  我還是頭一次穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的活兒完了再去做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼打掃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髒得一塌糊塗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會打掃自己屋子的殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來沒什麼魄力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事就交給我這個助手來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,500萬美元之外不足的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好地補回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  玲二  你有親人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天國就有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙親已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從那最臭最爛的死老爸那兒逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後朱荻把我撿了回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是這樣  我現在也不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是姐妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  唯一的親人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  朱荻卻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱荻死了之後  我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該上哪兒去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是死法  也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾  伸出手來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會珍惜它的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠珍惜它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有演員都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅耍小把戲利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還再度搞陰謀的克勞迪婭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一樣想吞併Inferno的梧桐大輔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及發覺了他們的陰謀並極力阻止的懷斯梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  還有新的演員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來造就這最宏偉的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  現在開始會忙起來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ein
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  那傢伙就是殺朱荻的兇手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也是一夥的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也見證吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  在儲水桶後面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行  梧桐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你真是嚇我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被射了嗎  打中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是擦了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要那麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何也想看清那傢伙的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得很好哦  觀察者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是殺朱荻的兇手  你報仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  馬上順C路線撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並等待我下一個指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我聽到一些傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodies的艾扎克死了那是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經報了仇了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的殺手修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話  這之後殺人的任務我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的任務就不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說我被炒了…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去你那廚藝就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還得讓你做我的炊事女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  太好了！女僕！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想試試看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕服很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  果然還是想成為玲二的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾  這…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦  玲二是不想讓我變成殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為玲二知道殺手的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾  你可以走上任何道路  可以幹任何工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏要當殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二討厭殺手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那連自己也討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全習慣了殺人  無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭的就是這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是玲二…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經壞了  你想變成我這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起  玲二…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾  我說太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是事實  不知道因為我而死了多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有我他們就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都能回到家人和戀人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是玲二的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二只是接下了必須有人去做的工作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這麼冠冕堂皇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玲二是很想殺人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想殺人而開槍的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡殺人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你殺過一次人  世界的一切都會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到的景色  聽到的聲音  一切都會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再像現在的凱爾這樣  溫柔地接受他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你該停留的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該來跟我一樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  但是玲二會一直在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我也過去的話  就能跟玲二一直在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想分開  想一直待在玲二身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幫上玲二的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟玲二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣  就能和你在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我會過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會過去玲二那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去  讓我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到凱爾所在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時間居然還有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天撿了一部壞掉了的錄影機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想試試能不能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買部新的不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣多浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能用…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早去早回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場合下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  有了  有畫面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  出租店還沒打烊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二  玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  玲二…玲二他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說好不會離開我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說好要跟我在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  他就是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都被蒙在鼓裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告  故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就哭出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能和以前一樣…
